   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y72.2 Var. a (mss. 40, 88, 400, 410 (sec. m.), 2007, 2010, 2030, 2101, 2106, 4000, 4010, 4040, 4050, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>hamistaiiaēca nižbərətaiiaēca aṇgrahe mańiiə̄uš</em> ēn gyāg pad harw <em>hamistaiiaēca</em> grih-ē abar barsom zanišn pad zōt ud rāspīg dō abar azabar ēk abar azēr</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "<em>hamistaiiaēca nižbərətaiiaēca aṇgrahe mańiiə̄uš</em>. At this passage, at each <em>hamistaiiaēca</em>,  knots have to be tied on the <em>barsom</em> together by the 
            <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em>: two above and one below."</ab>
         <ab>Y72.2 Var. b (ms. 5): </ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            pad <em>nižbərətaiiaēca</em> grih abar barsom zanišn zōt ud rāspīg harw dō guftan tā ō ī  <em>yə̄ hudā̊ yōi həṇti</em>.</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>nižbərətaiiaēca</em>, knots have to be tied on the <em>barsom</em>. The <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em>, both, should recite until <em>yə̄ hudā̊ yōi həṇti</em>"</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
